    "description": "Diner Together VR is a multiplayer co-op diner management simulator, you can play with up to 4 friends!<br><br>Own your own diner! cook, serve, clean, manage your finances, achieve good ratings and make your diner the best in the area!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Diner and Drive Thru</strong><br>There are two places where customers can arrive from, inside the diner and the drive thru, in the drive thru you will need to pack the order before giving it to the customer.<br>If the flow of customers is too much to handle you can close the drive thru.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/dbe9e2b4a6494fbf0dde4f8fc38d2669.poster.avif?t=1728582704\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/dbe9e2b4a6494fbf0dde4f8fc38d2669.webm?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/dbe9e2b4a6494fbf0dde4f8fc38d2669.mp4?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong> Several Types of Food</strong><br>There are many types of meats, fruits, vegetables, snacks, drinks, etc. All of which you can combine however you like!<br><br></li><li><strong> Randomly Generated Orders</strong><br>All of the orders ingredients and drinks are randomly generated.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/e177f3754d9862f3cd9c16e3de862ace.poster.avif?t=1728582704\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/e177f3754d9862f3cd9c16e3de862ace.webm?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/e177f3754d9862f3cd9c16e3de862ace.mp4?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong> Different Meals Per Day</strong><br>There are three meals per day: Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner. The customers orders change depending on which time of the day it is.<br><br></li><li><strong> Economy and Market</strong><br>Your ingredients will run out, so you will need to make sure to have enough money to buy more from the market!<br>Customers pay you according to order size, accuracy and how well it was cooked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/b65a5e8988d8f2a1eb942cb0d3e23c57.poster.avif?t=1728582704\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/b65a5e8988d8f2a1eb942cb0d3e23c57.webm?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1795670/extras/b65a5e8988d8f2a1eb942cb0d3e23c57.mp4?t=1728582704\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong> Cleaning</strong><br>After a few orders and with time you diner can start to become a little dirty, make sure to clean it once in a while so that more customer can enjoy the experience!</li></ul>",
